data.description: RARE, Beautiful Spacious 1 story home with an oversized 3 Car garage plumbed for sink in garage with exterior door to back yard, Extra 4 Feet extension and 3 garage door openers. East Facing. This customized home has a large open kitchen to living area with High ceilings, upgraded kitchen design, Open Sitting room in Master Bedroom as well as a formal study in front entry area. Primary Bathroom has a large walk in closet,  Open Custom Shower.  Eve lighting package,  Fenced in back yard with a covered patio and Sprinkler system. Tile Thru out most areas. Carpet in Bedrooms Only.  This is a wonderful home with extra driveway space with the 3 car garage.   I great find at this price in this Highly sought after neighborhood of Sant Rita Ranch.  Loaded with Resort style amenities. Acclaimed in neighborhood elementary and middle schools, Liberty Hill ISD.
